>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: PoP - Levels II.</span><hr size=1> I fully agree with you, and I see only one solution : SOE needs to remove the &quot;level gap penalty&quot;, id est the 2-levels step they introduce in the con system post 60.<br>
